          </div>
          <div class="ux-card__actions">
            <button class="ux-btn ux-btn--outline ux-btn--sm">
              <svg class="ux-btn__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3"/></svg>
              Descargar TXT
            </button>
            <button class="ux-btn ux-btn--outline ux-btn--sm">
              <svg class="ux-btn__icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1"/></svg>
              Copiar todos
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ux-card__body">
          <div class="cloud-codes">
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">01</span> 4F8K-X29Q-7HRT</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">02</span> 9ZJP-LW3M-BV62</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">03</span> RT4N-EXC8-K15D</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">04</span> H72S-FY4B-WP3X</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">05</span> Q83V-NM2L-YK57</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">06</span> 6CGT-AP9R-EZ41</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">07</span> S5BX-J8DH-T2VW</div>
            <div class="cloud-code"><span class="cloud-code__num">08</span> 1ULM-K9NE-PR84</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: var(--ux-space-3);">
        <div class="ux-callout ux-callout--warn">
          <span class="ux-callout__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.3 3.86l-8.52 14.7A2 2 0 0 0 3.5 22h17a2 2 0 0 0 1.72-3.45L13.7 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.4 0z"/></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="ux-callout__body">
            <p class="ux-callout__title">Guarda estos códigos antes de continuar</p>
            <p class="ux-callout__desc">Si pierdes el acceso a tu app autenticadora <strong>y</strong> a estos códigos, perderás permanentemente el acceso a tu cuenta de ERPlora Cloud. No podemos recuperarlos.</p>
            <label style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-top:10px;font-size:var(--ux-text-sm);color:var(--ux-ink-2);cursor:pointer;">
              <input type="checkbox" data-bind:codes-saved/>
              He copiado y guardado mis códigos de respaldo en un lugar seguro
            </label>
            <div class="ux-callout__actions">
              <a href="#" class="ux-callout__link">Más información sobre 2FA</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

  </div>
</div>


